title: ECSC Virginia Beach | Neff
description:
Virginia Beach hosted ECSC 2012. Neff was in attendance dishing out product to kids that waited in line for hours for a chance to spin the Neff Wheel. 

A great weekend of surfing was capped off with a live performance by Iration. 

Mr. Neff was also in attendance.
